{
  "stem": "10825.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we-- from Kiev, we were sent to a city Rostov that lies on the River Don, also a very well-known city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we gave-- there was a special [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] city-like or town for pilots.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was a pilot city in a special arrangement.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we gave there a concert.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was a Saturday night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And next day was Sunday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they wanted to reward us with something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they took us to the opera.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was given a-- a Ukrainian opera.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And after the first act, a military man came out and said that Germany went to war with Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The first city that was bombed was Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then we were stuck.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We couldn't do nothing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Whatever the-- wherever they would send us, we have to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we came back to Kiev, because Kiev was the capital.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave us a street-- a train car, a big train car.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were 50 people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they send us in groups.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They send us to sing for the military, for the echelons that went to the war and the-- the poor soldiers that came already wounded.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I was a soloist, and my late husband was the-- the pianist, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so they gave him an accordion.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we went as a team in one place.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other were sent in different places.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "At night, we-- we were taken from all those places back to the train car.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And if we have got to go somewheres, they-- they-- they took the train car, and then joined it to-- to the-- to a train where it went in that direction that we have got to go this way.",
      "word_count": 39
    }
  ],
